《'''确认死亡'''》（{{lang-en|''Confirmed Dead''}}）[[美国电视|美国]]电视剧《[[迷失|迷失]]》[[迷失_(第四季)|第4季]]的第2集，也是全剧的第74集，于2008年2月7日通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在美国首播，还通过[[CTV电视网|CTV电视网]]在加拿大[[首演|首播]]<ref>{{cite web | work = [[美国广播公司|ABC]] Medianet | date = 2008-01-18 | format = XLS | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120916212450/http://www.abcmedianet.com/primeschedule/ABCGRIDSJAN21FEB10.xls | url = http://www.abcmedianet.com/primeschedule/ABCGRIDSJAN21FEB10.xls | title = Primetime Program Schedule Grid | archivedate = 2012-09-16 | accessdate = 2012-09-16 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

从本集开始，节目中将新增两位主要角色，分别是[[肯·梁|肯·梁]]扮演的[[麦尔斯·斯特劳姆|麦尔斯·斯特劳姆]]和[[丽贝卡·马德尔|丽贝卡·马德尔]]饰演的[[夏洛特·路易斯|夏洛特·路易斯]]，杰夫·法赫诠释的次要角色[[法兰克·莱帕达斯|法兰克·莱帕达斯]]也是在本集中首次亮相。为了防止[[剧透|剧透]]或泄密，众演员试镜的场景都不是片中的真实镜头。马德尔和法赫同编剧起初设想的夏洛特和法兰克都有一定差异，但众编剧选择修改角色设定来让他们相符，麦尔斯一角同样为肯·梁做了调整。本集由[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]德鲁·高达和[[制作人|制作人]]布莱恩·{{lang|en|K}}·沃恩[[编剧|编剧]]，另一名执行制作人斯蒂芬·威廉姆斯[[导演|执导]]<ref name="press">{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2008-01-18 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=011808_12 | title = Four Strangers Arrive on the Island, Leading the Survivors to Question the Intentions of Their Supposed Rescuers | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212115500/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=011808_12 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-12-12 }}</ref>。

这集的剧情从2004年12月21日开始，距[[海洋航空|海洋航空]]815号航班坠毁已经过了91天，节目中的闪回镜头显示近海某货轮上有4人来到岛上。本集的主要内容是[[约翰·洛克_(迷失)|约翰·洛克]]带领一组人前往兵营，他也开始明白[[本杰明·莱纳斯|本杰明·莱纳斯]]（[[迈克尔·爱默生|迈克尔·爱默生]]饰）为什么会那么害怕那些刚刚来到岛上的人。《确认死亡》一共吸引了约1700万美国观众收看，并获得评论界的普遍好评，多位剧评人都称赞节目中新增人物的表现。<ref>{{cite web | publisher = ABC | title = 'Confirmed Dead': Season 4, Episode 402 Recap | date = 2008-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090811055059/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=recap#t=46481&d=80712 | deadurl = yes | url = http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=recap#t=46481&d=80712 | archivedate = 2009-08-11 | accessdate = 2009-08-11}}</ref>

== 剧情 ==
本集共有5段闪回镜头，分别讲述货轮上的船员同[[海洋航空|海洋航空]]815航班幸存者取得联系后的反应和行动。

* [[丹尼尔·法拉第|丹尼尔·法拉第]]（[[杰瑞米·戴维斯|杰瑞米·戴维斯]]饰）看到确认海洋航空815航班乘客全部遇难的新闻时哭了起来。旁边的人问他为何哭泣，他回答说自己也不知道。
* [[麦尔斯·斯特劳姆|麦尔斯·斯特劳姆]]（肯·梁）是个[[灵媒|灵媒]]，一位老妇人请他出手驱逐她孙女儿家中的鬼魂。麦尔斯与鬼魂交谈后发现一些藏匿的现金和毒品。
* [[夏洛特·路易斯|夏洛特·路易斯]]（[[丽贝卡·马德尔|丽贝卡·马德尔]]饰）是[[人类学|人类学家]]，她在突尼斯的沙漠里找到一具[[北极熊|北极熊]]骨架，上面还套有[[达摩计划|达摩计划]]的项圈。
* [[法兰克·莱帕达斯|法兰克·莱帕达斯]]（杰夫·法赫饰）是815航班原计划的飞行员，现在则是个酒鬼。他在看到乘客全部遇难的新闻时拨打海洋航空热线电话，声称电视上飞机残骸的镜头是伪造的。
* [[迷失角色列表|纳奥米·杜丽]]（玛莎·托马森饰）向雇主马修·亚巴顿（[[兰斯·雷迪克|兰斯·雷迪克]]饰）表示不满，觉得对方为自己挑选的同事很不理想。<ref name="episode">{{cite episode | credits = Goddard, Drew (writer) & Vaughan, Brian K. (writer) & Williams, Stephen (director) | title = Confirmed Dead | series = ''[[迷失|Lost]]'' | network = ABC | number = [[迷失剧集列表|2]] | season = [[迷失_(第四季)|4]] | date = 2008-02-07}}</ref>

由于直升机出现故障，丹尼尔用[[降落伞|降落伞]]落到岛上，然后用纳奥米的卫星电话同船上的乔治·明可夫斯基取得联系<ref>{{cite episode | credits = [[戴蒙·林道夫|Lindelof, Damon]] (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & [[杰克·本德|Bender, Jack]] (director) | title = The Constant | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 5 | season = 4 | date = 2008-02-28}}</ref>。次日清晨（2004年12月22日），815航班的幸存者[[杰克·谢泼德|杰克·谢泼德]]（[[马修·福克斯|马修·福克斯]]饰）和[[凯特·奥斯顿|凯特·奥斯顿]]（[[伊万杰琳·莉莉|伊万杰琳·莉莉]]饰）开始帮丹尼尔寻找同僚，另一边由[[约翰·洛克_(迷失)|约翰·洛克]]（[[特瑞·欧奎恩|特瑞·欧奎恩]]饰）带领的一组人也在找那些人。杰克和凯特找到麦尔斯，后者要求一定要看到纳奥米的尸体，并且坚持认为她肯定是被洛克所杀。洛克一行找到夏洛特并将之俘虏，还毁掉了她带的追踪装置。直升机驾驶员弗兰克向天上发射照明弹，杰克等人据此找到他。弗兰克表示，直升机安全降落，没有受到破坏。麦尔斯发现[[茱莉叶·柏克|茱莉叶·柏克]]（[[伊丽莎白·米切尔|伊丽莎白·米切尔]]饰）正是“其他人”之一，于是要求知道[[本杰明·莱纳斯|本]]（[[迈克尔·爱默生|迈克尔·爱默生]]饰）的下落，称找到他才是货轮船员的主要目标。<ref name="episode" />

洛克透露自己是遵照[[沃特·劳伊德|沃特·劳伊德]]（[[马尔科姆·大卫·凯利|马尔科姆·大卫·凯利]]）的指示带领众人前去兵营，但沃特早在1个多月前就离开了这座岛，所以有多人对洛克的做法不满<ref>{{cite episode | credits = Lindelof, Damon (writer) & Cuse, Carlton (writer) & Bender, Jack (director) | title = Live Together, Die Alone  | series = ''Lost'' | network = ABC | number = 24 | season = [[迷失_(第二季)|2]] | airdate = 2007-05-24}}</ref>，而且质疑洛克为什么不杀掉本。洛克用枪指住本，本则开始透露货轮上船员的信息，特别是夏洛特的身份，原来本在船上还派有间谍。<ref name="episode" />

== 制作 ==
[[File:Jeff_Fahey.jpg|thumb]]》]]

为了防止[[剧透|剧透]]及其它方面泄密，《迷失》的[[执行制作人|执行制作人]]、编剧兼节目统筹[[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]和卡尔顿·库斯（{{lang|en|Carlton Cuse}}）用“货轮佬”来指代丹尼尔、夏洛特、麦尔斯和弗兰克<ref name="ew">{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2008-02-20 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20179125_5,00.html |title='Lost': Mind-Blowing Scoop From Its Producers |publisher=''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129025908/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20179125_5%2C00.html |accessdate=2014-11-29 |archivedate=2014-11-29 }}</ref>，并且在为这些角色挑选演员时还临时使用假的人名、职业和镜头内容<ref>{{cite news | last = Littleton | first = Cynthia | title = “Lost”: The weight of the wait | work = ''[[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]]'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131001120427/http://variety.com/2007/more/news/lost-the-weight-of-the-wait-1117974014/ | url = http://variety.com/2007/more/news/lost-the-weight-of-the-wait-1117974014/ | archivedate = 2013-10-01 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-08 | date = 2007-10-12}}</ref>。肯·梁曾于2007年4月在{{lang|en|[[HBO|HBO]]}}电视剧《[[黑道家族|黑道家族]]》中[[友情客串|客串出镜]]，林道夫和库斯看到他的演出后特意为之创作了麦尔斯一角<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-08-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129025902/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20053863%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-11-29 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20053863,00.html |title=''Lost'': Five Fresh Faces |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-11-29 }}</ref>，不过起初的新闻报道中称，梁扮演的角色名叫“罗素”（{{lang|en|Russell}}），是个“天才数学家”<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-08-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130929165709/http://www.tvguide.com/news/exclusive-sopranos-scene-stealer-8359.aspx | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/exclusive-sopranos-scene-stealer-8359/ | title = Exclusive: Sopranos Scene-stealer Gets Lost! | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2015-09-08 | publisher = [[CBS互动|CBS Interactive]] | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-09-29}}</ref>。林道夫等人觉得为梁的角色起个听起来很像“[[涡流|涡流]]”（{{lang|en|Maelstrom}}）的名字会很“酷”，所以将角色的姓名定为“麦尔斯·斯特劳姆”（{{lang|en|Miles Straume}}）<ref name="ew" />。林道夫和库斯还称，如果梁没有接演，那么他们就会取消这个角色，另行创作一个截然不同的新人物。梁起初和剧组签下常见客串演员的合同，他曾在接受采访时表示：“麦尔斯不擅社交，这太棒了，因为我也是。”<ref>{{cite web | last = Malcolm | first = Shawna | date = 2008-02-07 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-new-characters-38564/ | title = ''Lost'' Exclusive: Meet Four New Characters! | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2015-09-08 | archivedate = 2012-10-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013004617/http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-new-characters-38564.aspx}}</ref>。服装设计师罗兰·桑切斯（{{lang|en|Roland Sanchez}}）非常喜欢[[基思·理查兹|基思·理查兹]]身穿一件无袖背心的形象，所以想把其中一个“货轮佬”按理查兹的形象设计。桑切斯觉得麦尔斯的个人形象应该比较憔悴，他还买了件[[阿玛尼|阿玛尼]]外套，剪掉衣袖，再加上帽子，梁就是以这身装扮在剧中亮相<ref>{{cite video | last = Sanchez | first = Roland | date = 2008-02-08 | url = http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast | title = The Official ''Lost'' Video Podcast | publisher = ABC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080325233329/http://abc.go.com/primetime/lost/index?pn=podcast | accessdate = 2008-03-25 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2008-03-25}}</ref>。执行制作人兼编剧[[爱德华·基齐斯|爱德华·基齐斯]]（{{lang|en|Edward Kitsis}}）曾连续多年提议把某个角色起名叫“拉皮德斯”（{{lang|en|Lapidus}}），这个愿望到[[迷失_(第三季)|第3季]]第14集《[[报告_(迷失)|报告]]》（{{lang|en|''Exposé''}}）中才实现，剧中有个没有露面的人物名叫里克·拉皮德斯（{{lang|en|Rick Lapidus}}）<ref>{{cite video | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_409_audio_podcast_8ea5441e-65f4-4d96-ad4d-4e2de171b95e_1604375.mp3 | title = The Official LOST Audio Podcast | website = American Broadcasting Company (ABC.com) | people = Cuse, Carlton; Lindelof, Damon | date = 2008-03-21 | archivedate = 2013-07-19 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2013-07-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130719220941/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_409_audio_podcast_8ea5441e-65f4-4d96-ad4d-4e2de171b95e_1604375.mp3 | format = MP3}}</ref>。但是，基齐斯对此并不满意，直升机驾驶员弗兰克·拉皮德斯（{{lang|en|Frank Lapidus}}）由此诞生<ref name="ew" />。据几位节目统筹表示，常见客串演员杰夫·法赫是该角色的第一人选，也是唯一人选；他们还表示，法赫的眼神很“强烈”，他在感性方面非常适合这个角色<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-08-27 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20053479,00.html |title='Lost' Scoop: Jeff Fahey Joins Cast |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-11-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129210356/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20053479%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-11-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。法赫这时留了很长的胡子，但原本设想中的弗兰克是没有胡子的，为此林德曼和库斯决定让法赫保留胡须。两位制作人还表示，弗兰克“觉得什么事情背后都可能有阴谋，从来不相信有任何事情就真的是像一眼看去的那个样子，估计他应该每集《[[X档案|X档案]]》都看过，为此他将受益匪浅。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Keck | first = Will | date = 2008-02-13 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/celebwatch/2008-02-13-mader-sidebar_N.htm | title = Meet Three More of the 'Freighter People' from ''Lost'' | work = ''[[今日美国|USA Today]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019195658/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/celebwatch/2008-02-13-mader-sidebar_N.htm | archivedate = 2012-10-19}}</ref>

丽贝卡·马德尔的试镜片段是一段闪回镜头，但并不是节目中的剧情，所以没有采用，对此她深感失望<ref>{{cite video | author = SBK & Cabin Boy | date = 2008-02-29 | title = ''Lost'' Interview with Charlotte (Rebecca Mader) | work = WTKS-FM}}</ref>。角色的姓名夏洛特·路易斯在本集播出数月前就遭剧透泄露。根据原本的设想，夏洛特是美国人<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | title = Lost Newbie to Kristen Bell: "Thanks for Turning Down Charlotte!" | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | first = Michael | date = 2008-02-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120719110943/http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-newbie-to-8462.aspx | archivedate = 2012-07-19 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-newbie-to-8462/}}</ref>，但编剧们觉得马德尔模仿的美国口音效果不及她自然的英国口音，夏洛特因此变成英国人，库斯还称马德尔就像“年轻版的[[妮可·基德曼|妮可·基德曼]]”<ref>{{cite news|title=''Lost'' producers on their five new actors |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2015-09-09 |last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=2007-08-29 |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2007/09/03/lost-producers-their-five-new-actors/2 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129223957/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20053863_2%2C00.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-11-29 }}</ref>。挑选演员期间，剧组声称夏洛特是位“成功的学者”<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2007-08-01 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-introduces-8447/ | title = Lost Introduces the Other Others!? | work = ''TV Guide'' | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | archivedate = 2013-09-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130927165403/http://www.tvguide.com/news/lost-introduces-8447.aspx}}</ref>。选角期间还一度出现谣传，称剧组主动联系[[克里斯汀·贝尔|克里斯汀·贝尔]]出演夏洛特<ref>{{cite news | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2008-08-08 | title = 'Ask Ausiello' on ''Lost'', ''Friday Night Lights'', ''Bones'' and More! | work = ''TV Guide''}}</ref>，实际上贝尔只是和制作人就参加演出有过交流，但剧组并没有主要邀请她出演任何角色<ref>{{cite web | last = Kubicek | first = John | date = 2007-10-16 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/heroes/heroes-exclusive-kristen-bell-12506.aspx | title = ''Heroes'' Exclusive: Kristen Bell and Tim Kring Reveal Season 2 Spoilers | work = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150713012044/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/heroes/heroes-exclusive-kristen-bell-12506.aspx | archivedate = 2015-07-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。马德尔此前还从未看过《迷失》，但她却决心要让林道夫和库斯都对自己的试镜感到满意，否则就不会走出试镜室<ref>{{cite news | last = Kexk | first = Will | date = 2008-02-24 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019195537/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/celebwatch/2008-02-24-Rebecca-Mader_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/celebwatch/2008-02-24-Rebecca-Mader_N.htm | title = Mader Makes Her Mark as Latest ''Lost'' Cast Member | work = ''USA Today'' | accessdate = 2015-09-09}}</ref>。随后马德尔就开始观看《迷失》的前3季，看到第1季第4集《[[丛林流浪|丛林流浪]]》时得知自己入选成为夏洛特的扮演者<ref name="ugo">{{cite web | last = Lachonis | first = Jon "DocArzt" | date = 2008-02-13 | url = http://www.ugo.com/tv/lost/?cur=rebecca-mader | title = Rebecca Mader ''Lost'' Interview | work = UGO Networks | accessdate = 2009-01-23 | archivedate = 2009-01-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090123143118/http://www.ugo.com/tv/lost/?cur=rebecca-mader | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。马德尔同剧组签订常见客串演员的合同，并在接下来2到3周里继续观看前3季的其它剧集，看完第3季季终集《[[透过窥镜|透过窥镜]]》数小时后就开始参加《确认死亡》的演出，拍摄夏洛特遇到洛克等人的一组镜头。除了告诉马德尔，夏洛特“一定程度上就像女性版的[[印第安纳·琼斯|印第安纳·琼斯]]”外，编剧和制作人都没有向她透露角色的细节。对于马德尔来说，出演一个既不知背景，又不明动机的人物是件极具挑战，但又非常有趣的事。夏洛特的全名叫夏洛特·斯台普斯·路易斯（{{lang|en|Charlotte Staples Lewis}}），这个名字是在向以《[[纳尼亚传奇|纳尼亚传奇]]》和多部[[基督教|基督教]]相关著作闻名的作家[[C·S·路易斯|克利夫·斯特普尔斯·路易斯]]致敬。路易斯是马德尔童年时最喜欢的作家之一，她觉得自己出演的角色能以这位作家命名是件既“邪恶”又“很酷”的事。<ref>{{cite web | last = Porter | first = Rick | date = 2008-02-13 | url = http://zap2it.com/2008/02/good-charlotte-rebecca-mader-talks-lost/ | archivedate = 2009-01-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090130144631/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2008/02/good-charlotte.html | title = Good(?) Charlotte: Rebecca Mader Talks ''Lost'' | work = Zap2it | accessdate = 2015-09-09}}</ref>马德尔还对角色在化妆和头发上需要的工作量很少感到高兴，称自己就是想要粗犷一些，“我想拿着枪在泥里打滚<ref>{{cite news | last = Nichols | first = Katherine | date = 2008-02-19 | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150907011321/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2008/02/19/features/story01.html | archivedate = 2015-09-07 | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2008/02/19/features/story01.html | title = Hero or ... ''Lost'' Actress Rebecca Mader is Clueless About Her Character's Motivation But Loves the Role | newspaper = ''Honolulu Star-Bulletin''}}</ref>”。对于参与《迷失》的拍摄工作，马德尔声称自己“一辈子都没这么开心过”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dos Santos | first = Kristin | date = 2008-02-08 | title = ''Lost'': Meet the New Girl | publisher = E! | accessdate = 2008-06-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080630065647/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=c628ccf6-3cf0-413d-938e-d690942fb0b6 | archivedate = 2008-06-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=c628ccf6-3cf0-413d-938e-d690942fb0b6}}</ref>。根据本集剧情，夏洛特生于1979年7月2日。但[[迷失_(第五季)|第5季]]第8集《[[拉弗勒_(迷失)|拉弗勒]]》（{{lang|en|''LaFleur''}}）的剧情又表明夏洛特1974年时已经是个小女孩，两者相互矛盾，出现时间连续性错误。林道夫和库斯对此在播客中表示，《确认死亡》的剧本中原本将夏洛特的生日定在1970年，但马德尔不希望观众觉得她的实际年龄要比看起来老很多，所以要求做出更改。不过，马德尔之后在[[博客|博客]]中表示，提议做出此项更改的是剧本协调员格雷格·内森斯（{{lang|en|Gregg Nations}}）。库斯和林道夫此后也改口称马德尔的说法是正确的。<ref>{{cite podcast | title = The Official LOST Audio Podcast: March 19th, 2009 | website = American Broadcasting Company (ABC.com). | host = Cuse, Carlton; Lindelof, Damon | date = 2009-03-19 | accessdate = 2012-02-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120218232152/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_510_audio_podcast_5de8e99f-8d9b-410b-a8bb-9393a9f91e0f_2041378.mp3 | archivedate = 2012-02-18 | format = MP3 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_510_audio_podcast_5de8e99f-8d9b-410b-a8bb-9393a9f91e0f_2041378.mp3}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ausiellofiles.ew.com/2009/03/lost-exclusive.html |title='Lost' exclusive: War erupts over Charlotte's real age! |author=Ausiello, Michael |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |date=2009-03-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327090747/http://ausiellofiles.ew.com/2009/03/lost-exclusive.html |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-03-27 |archivedate=2009-03-27 }}</ref>

本集大部分镜头都是在2007年9月11至23日间拍摄<ref>{{cite news | last = Perez | first = Mario | date = 2008-09-11 | title = Jeremy Davies, Matthew Fox and Evangeline Lilly Asset Display Photography Caption Information | work = ABC Medianet}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Harada | first = Wayne | date = 2008-09-27 | archivedate = 2015-05-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150507182250/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2007/Sep/27/il/hawaii709270313.html | url = http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2007/Sep/27/il/hawaii709270313.html | title = 'Lost' Takes Over Cassis, Brings Chinatown Snow | newspaper = ''Honolulu Advertiser'' | accessdate = 2015-09-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，并与下一集的拍摄工作重叠<ref>{{cite news | last = Perez | first = Mario | date = 2008-09-19 | title = Jeff Fahey Asset Display Photography Caption Information | work = ABC Medianet}}</ref>。剧集主要是在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]][[欧胡岛|欧胡岛]]取景，其中突尼斯沙漠的镜头是在采石场拍摄，用工业风扇刮起假的沙子<ref name="ugo" />。每集《迷失》剧集通常会有约50个[[视觉效果|视觉效果]]镜头，这其中有些完全由特效制作，有些是由特效和真实拍摄相结合。这集开头的815航班水下残骸，以及从丹尼尔的视角拍摄他从直升机上跳伞着陆的镜头均属视觉特效。弗兰克的闪回戏段中有他抛出一架玩具飞机，飞机盘旋着飞入小鱼缸的镜头。剧组起初并没打算在这段镜头里采用特技，但据特效总监米奇·萨斯金（{{lang|en|Mitch Suskin}}）表示，根本没有别的办法能让玩具飞机真的就这样飞进鱼缸里去。摄制组先准备水缸，在底部放一些石块，装满水进行拍摄，再在后期剪辑时把飞机加进去。萨斯金表示，《确认死亡》的特效制作相对而言比较“清闲”，因为后期制作开始后，节目还要过4个多月才会播出，所以时间非常充裕。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Raugust | first = Karen | date = 2008-03-04 | accessdate = 2008-09-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080917175142/http://vfxworld.com/?atype=articles&id=3568 | archivedate = 2008-09-17 | url = http://vfxworld.com/?atype=articles&id=3568 | title = ''Lost'': Season 4 – VFX Interrupts | journal = VFXWorld | deadurl = yes}}</ref>

2007年秋，《迷失》的一众编剧向美国广播公司高层提出构想，其主要内容为“克里斯蒂安一世号”（{{lang|en|Christiane I}}）打捞船在[[爪哇海沟|爪哇海沟]]寻找“黑岩”和类似815航班残骸的其它多种物品。美国广播公司为此花费300万美元，聘请澳大利亚某公司设计[[病毒营销|病毒营销]][[另类实境游戏|另类实境游戏]]《[[寻找815航班|寻找815航班]]》（{{lang|en|''Find 815''}}）。<ref>{{cite news|last=Sinclair |first=Lara |title=Lost fans reunite in drama online |newspaper=''The Australian'' |accessdate=2008-02-17 |date=2008-02-14 |url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,23209038-26077,00.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20080217225645/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,23209038-26077,00.html |archivedate=2008-02-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>游戏设计完成后，美国广播公司首先通过旗下的{{lang|en|Medianet}}网站发布新闻稿，宣布海洋航空公司“重新开始营业”，《寻找815航班》随即在2007年12月28日上线，一直运营到2008年1月31日<ref>{{cite news|last=La Gesse |first=Bobby |date=2008-01-17 |title='Lost' billboard purchaser ordered 'vandalism' |newspaper=''Ames Tribune'' |publisher=Iowa Newspapers |url=http://www.midiowanews.com/site/tab1.cfm?newsid=19182861&BRD=2700&PAG=461&dept_id=554432&rfi=6 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20080121020734/http://www.midiowanews.com/site/tab1.cfm?newsid=19182861&BRD=2700&PAG=461&dept_id=554432&rfi=6 |accessdate=2008-01-21 |archivedate=2008-01-21 }}</ref>。这款游戏围绕海洋航空技师山姆·托马斯（{{lang|en|Sam Thomas}}）展开，他的女友就在815航班上。托马斯收到“麦克斯韦集团”（{{lang|en|The Maxwell Group}}，《迷失》中威德摩尔实业的分支，但没有在电视剧中提及）发来的神秘电邮，然后成为“克里斯蒂安一世号”打捞船的一员，最终发现815航班残骸。<ref>{{cite news | last = Connelly | first = Michael Alan | date = 2008-01-31 | url = http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/01/we_decode_the_lost_online_game.html | title = We Decode the 'Lost' Online Game for You | work = ''New York'' | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521192228/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/01/we_decode_the_lost_online_game.html | archivedate = 2011-05-21}}</ref>《寻找815航班》是同电视剧分开制作，没有节目编剧的参与，所以游戏中的内容和电视剧存在相互矛盾的地方<ref>{{cite video | people = Lindelof, Damon & Cuse, Carlton | date = 2008-03-10 | archivedate = 2012-02-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210185441/http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_407_audio_podcast_2639b9f3-d701-4360-b0d4-ae298886bd2d_1591126.mp3 | title = Official ''Lost'' Audio Podcast | format = MP3 | url = http://ll.media.abc.com/podcast/audio/itunes/LOST_407_audio_podcast_2639b9f3-d701-4360-b0d4-ae298886bd2d_1591126.mp3 | website = ABC | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。《确认死亡》中找到815航班残骸的男子名叫“罗恩”（{{lang|en|Ron}}），但游戏中没有这个人，同时电视剧中也没有提及托马斯。林道夫和库斯表示，游戏中并不包括电视剧[[虛構世界|虛構世界]]的实际框架信息，很大程度上不过是给剧迷在两季间隙期送去一点消遣<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2008-02-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141130005727/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20179125_4%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-11-30 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20179125_4,00.html |title='Lost': Mind-Blowing Scoop From Its Producers |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2014-11-30 }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
《确认死亡》于2008年1月31日通过美国广播公司在美国首播，收看首播或是先行预录，并在播出后6小时内观看的美国观众人数共有1529万，在该周电视节目中排名第7<ref>{{cite web | work = ABC Medianet | date = 2008-02-12 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=021208_04 | title = Weekly Program Rankings | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110929062051/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=021208_04 | accessdate = 2011-09-29 | archivedate = 2011-09-29 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。如果加上首播7天后观看预录的人数，则观众数会升至1696万<ref>{{cite web | last = Gorman | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | first = Bill | date = 2008-02-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120905222032/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/25/top-timeshifted-broadcast-shows-february-4-10/2753/ | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2008/02/25/top-timeshifted-broadcast-shows-february-4-10/2753/ | title = Top Time-Shifted Broadcast Shows, Feb 4–10 | work = TV by the Numbers | archivedate = 2012-09-05 }}</ref>。[[尼尔森收视率|尼尔森收视率]]调查结果显示，本集在18至49岁年龄段观众群中取得的收视率为6.5/16，这意味着全美所有该年龄段人群里有6.5%观看节目首播，而当时有看电视的该年龄段观众群中则有16%选择收看《确认死亡》<ref>{{cite web | work = ''ABC Medianet'' | date = 2008-02-12 | url = http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=021208_03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210142838/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=021208_03 | deadurl = yes | title = Weekly Primetime Ratings Report | accessdate = 2012-02-10 | archivedate = 2012-02-10}}</ref>。节目通过[[CTV电视网|CTV电视网]]在加拿大首播期间吸引了170.2万观众，在该周排名第6<ref>{{cite web | work = BBM Canada | date = 2008-02-12 | url = http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat02042008.pdf | title = Top Programs – Total Canada (English) | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090326080147/http://www.bbm.ca/en/nat02042008.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-26 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。英国则有120万人收看这集，比本季开局《[[结局的开始|结局的开始]]》的成绩还要好<ref>{{cite news | last = Holmwood | first = Leigh | date = 2008-02-18 | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | title = Kingdom reigns over The Last Enemy | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/feb/18/tvratings.television | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150621102247/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/feb/18/tvratings.television | newspaper = ''[[卫报|The Guardian]]'' | archivedate = 2015-06-21}}</ref>。本集在澳大利亚首播时只有85.3万观众收看，在该周所有电视节目里排第71位<ref>{{cite news | last = Dale | first = David | date = 2008-02-21 | archivedate = 2012-03-23 | deadurl = yes | url = http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/02/the_ratings_rac_75.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120323191701/http://blogs.sunherald.com.au/whoweare/archives/2008/02/the_ratings_rac_75.html | title = The Who We Are update: Week 8 | newspaper = ''The Sun-Herald''}}</ref>。

2008年1月28日，美国多位评论家拿到《结局的开始》和《确认死亡》的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}，还有附言请他们不要在评论中透露节目的主要剧情。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的玛丽·麦克纳马拉（{{lang|en|Mary McNamara}}）<ref>{{cite news | last = McNamara | first = Mary | date = 2008-01-31 | newspaper = ''[[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]]'' | url = http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2008/Feb/01/en/hawaii802010327.html | title = ''Lost'' in the Moment | via = The Honolulu Advertiser | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-09-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120907212635/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2008/Feb/01/en/hawaii802010327.html}}</ref>、《[[纽约邮报|纽约邮报]]》的亚当·巴克曼（{{lang|en|Adam Buckman}}）<ref>{{cite news|last=Buckman |first=Adam |date=2008-01-31 |archivedate=2012-10-18 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |url = http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/item_k1L73N4707XzxCaUPQ77zM;jsessionid=6589F9CE46D85F14BEBF89DC7A32FA7B |title=Island Fever: Thank God, At Least ''Lost'' is Back |newspaper=''[[纽约邮报|New York Post]]'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018152935/http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/item_k1L73N4707XzxCaUPQ77zM%3Bjsessionid%3D6589F9CE46D85F14BEBF89DC7A32FA7B |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的莫琳·瑞恩（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2015-07-15 | last = Ryan | first = Maureen | date = 2008-01-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/01/lost-shockers-a.html | title = ''Lost''<nowiki>'</nowiki>s Fab Start to Season 4, and a Chat with Co-Creator Damon Lindelof | newspaper = ''[[芝加哥论坛报|Chicago Tribune]]'' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150715214224/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/01/lost-shockers-a.html | accessdate = 2015-09-07}}</ref>、《[[新闻日报|新闻日报]]》（{{lang|en|''Newsday''}}）的黛安·韦茨（{{lang|en|Diane Werts}}）<ref>{{cite news|last=Werts |first=Diane |date=2008-01-30 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2008-04-30 |url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/tv/ny-ettell5555593jan30,0,2205345.column |accessdate=2008-04-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430215549/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/tv/ny-ettell5555593jan30%2C0%2C2205345.column |title=Review: ''Lost'' Finds Itself Again in New Season |newspaper=''Newsday'' }}</ref>，以及《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的蒂姆·古德曼（{{lang|en|Tim Goodman}}）都给予《确认死亡》正面评价<ref>{{cite news | last = Goodman | first = Tim | date = 2008-01-30 | title = Want to Get ''Lost''?  There's Still Time as Season Starts | newspaper = ''[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]]'' | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | archivedate = 2014-11-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129022755/http://www.sfgate.com/tv/article/WANT-TO-GET-LOST-THERE-S-STILL-TIME-AS-SEASON-3230470.php | | url = http://www.sfgate.com/tv/article/WANT-TO-GET-LOST-THERE-S-STILL-TIME-AS-SEASON-3230470.php}}</ref>。据{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}网站的奥斯卡·达尔（{{lang|en|Oscar Dahl}}）表示，这集“几乎赢得《迷失》剧迷的普遍喜爱<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | title = Lost: "Confirmed Dead" Reader Reactions | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120111120041/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-confirmed-dead-reader-rea-16535.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-confirmed-dead-reader-rea-16535.aspx | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | date = 2008-02-11 | archivedate = 2012-01-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>”，同时{{lang|en|UGO}}网站的乔恩·拉索尼斯（{{lang|en|Jon Lachonis}}）也称，剧中的几个新角色同样深受剧迷欢迎<ref name="ugo" />。

艾伦·塞平沃尔（{{lang|en|Alan Sepinwall}}）在《[[明星纪事报|明星纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Star-Ledger''}}）撰文称，《确认死亡》的开局表现一般，虽然剧情依然充实，4个新常见角色的背景、甚至来到岛上的真正原因都通过闪回镜头向观众交待清楚，但是节目并不能让人产生像《结局的开始》那样的情感共鸣。不过他也承认，不可能每一集都能面面俱到<ref>{{cite news | last = Sepinwall | first = Alan | date = 2008-02-07 | newspaper = ''The Star-Ledger'' | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203111628/http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/02/lost_confirmed_dead_who_ya_gon.html | url = http://blog.nj.com/alltv/2008/02/lost_confirmed_dead_who_ya_gon.html | title = Lost, "Confirmed Dead": Who ya gonna call? Miles! | archivedate = 2014-02-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》周刊的詹姆斯·波尼沃兹克（{{lang|en|James Poniewozik}}）表示，本集剧情发展的效率和精准令人惊叹，从货轮到达岛上的4人出场时间都很短，并且每人都只有一段闪回镜头，但到节目结束时，观众却已经对这些人有了真正的了解<ref>{{cite news | last = Poniewozik | first = James | date = 2008-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080319111909/http://www.time-blog.com/tuned_in/2008/02/lostwatch_weve_got_company.html | url = http://www.time-blog.com/tuned_in/2008/02/lostwatch_weve_got_company.html | title = Lostwatch: We've Got Company | archivedate = 2008-03-19 | accessdate = 2008-03-19 | publisher = [[时代_(杂志)|Time]]}}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的杰夫·詹森（{{lang|en|Jeff Jensen}}）认为，《确认死亡》“拥有令人着迷的新角色，带来让人叹为观止的众多可能和激动人心的新理论素材”，但他也指出，有部分评论认为这集还是存在缺陷，剧中丹尼尔只是从电视上看到815航班的残骸，所以这有可能是伪造的；弗兰克何以能令直升机安全降落的谜题未解，纳奥米一角已经死亡，但却出现她的闪回镜头，这有违《迷失》的惯例，此外，本对洛克的操纵情节在这集已经显得有些过火。<ref>{{cite news|last=Jensen |first=Jeff "Doc" |date=2008-02-07 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20177008,00.html |title=Chute First, Ask Questions Later |work=''Entertainment Weekly'' |accessdate=2015-01-01 |archivedate=2015-01-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101030549/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20177008%2C00.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>{{lang|en|[[E!|E!]]}}频道的克里斯汀·多斯·桑托斯（{{lang|en|Kristin Dos Santos}}）称自己看到爪哇海沟中815航班的残骸镜头时惊呼“我的妈呀！”她还觉得剧中茱莉叶和凯特取笑杰克的情节非常搞笑，并且很高兴能够再度看到飞行员<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Dos Santos | first1 = Kristin | last2 = Godwin | first2 = Jennifer | date = 2008-02-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080424062029/http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=0f9b7623-0229-4af4-a33d-f51749d5f973 | title = ''Lost'' Redux: Welcome, New People! (Please Don't Shoot the Losties) | publisher = E! | url = http://www.eonline.com/gossip/kristin/detail/index.jsp?uuid=0f9b7623-0229-4af4-a33d-f51749d5f973 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2008-04-24 | archivedate = 2008-04-24}}</ref>。妮琪·斯塔福德（{{lang|en|Nikki Stafford}}）在《[[向导_(杂志)|向导]]》（{{lang|en|''Wizard''}}）杂志发文，称赞丹尼尔用降落伞着陆桥段的镜头处理，“你可以感觉到他在空中自由落体期间的慌乱，时而看看头上的降落伞，时而又看着脚下自己马上会撞到的树……这真是棒极了”<ref>{{cite journal | last = Stafford | first = Nikki | date = 2008-02-08 | title = We Meet the 'Rescuers' ... and Find Out Who They're Really Here For | journal = ''Wizard''}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站的里斯·卡拉博特（{{lang|en|Chris Carabott}}）给予本集的评分为8（最高10分），他在评论中写道：“无论从任何方面来说，这集都不会让人失望，但由于其中需要介绍4个新角色，其它方面肯定会有所欠缺。”他还称赞几位新角色的演出，称“梁充分表现出麦尔斯信心十足之下的那种傲慢，戴维斯也完美呈现了法拉第的尴尬举止。法赫在诠释莱帕达斯方面表现优异，甚至在一定程度上掩盖了常见角色的光芒。”<ref>{{cite web | last = Carabott | first = Chris | date = 2008-02-06 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/02/06/lost-confirmed-dead-advance-review | title = Lost: "Confirmed Dead" Advance Review: Four New Characters Join the Cast | publisher = IGN | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150101054009/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/02/06/lost-confirmed-dead-advance-review | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | archivedate = 2015-01-01}}</ref>[[美国在线|美国在线]]电视小队的艾琳·马特尔（{{lang|en|Erin Martell}}）表示，“观看《确认死亡》就像在看我所梦想的《迷失》剧集，人们终于会直截了当地提出问题了……不过这集讲的全都是那些船员”<ref>{{cite web | last = Martell | first = Erin | date = 2008-02-08 | url = http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/02/08/lost-confirmed-dead | title = Lost: Confirmed Dead | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110521150712/http://www.tvsquad.com/2008/02/08/lost-confirmed-dead/ | work = TV Squad | accessdate = 2011-05-21 | archivedate = 2011-05-21 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。节目在电视上首播次日，{{lang|en|BuddyTV}}网站的达尔声称观众“经历了一段史诗般的旅程，其娱乐性和引人入胜的程度与以往任何电视剧相比也不逞多让”<ref>{{cite web | last = Dahl | first = Oscar | date = 2008-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150101030331/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-the-unexpected-adventure-16483.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/lost/lost-the-unexpected-adventure-16483.aspx | title = The Unexpected Adventure | work = ''BuddyTV'' | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | archivedate = 2015-01-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。但《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》的[[迈克尔·奥西亚罗|迈克尔·奥西亚罗]]（{{lang|en|Michael Ausiello}}）显然不这么认为，称节目中虽然有不少出色的方面，但总体而言负面部分还是比较多。他对[[克莱尔·李特顿|克莱尔·李特顿]]（[[艾蜜莉·迪瑞文|艾蜜莉·迪瑞文]]饰）得知[[查理·佩斯|查理·佩斯]]（[[多米尼克·莫纳汉|多米尼克·莫纳汉]]饰）溺毙后表现得并不伤心感到不满，还觉得杰克花了太长时间才发现货轮船员的主要目标。<ref>{{cite web | last = Ausiello | first = Michael | date = 2008-02-07 | archivedate = 2012-10-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013004632/http://www.tvguide.com/news/Big-Problems-Weeks-8078.aspx | deadurl = no | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/big-problems-weeks-8078/ | title = My Big Problem(s) With This Week's ''Lost'' | work = ''TV Guide'' | accessdate = 2015-09-10 }}</ref>[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]网站的本·劳森-琼斯（{{lang|en|Ben Rawson-Jones}}）给予《确认死亡》的评级为3星（最高5星），认为节目“马马虎虎”，但“节目中提供的新启示还是相当惊人的”，让观众可以一时不再为之前剧情中太多的谜团伤透脑筋<ref>{{cite web | last = Rawson-Jones | first = Ben | date = 2008-02-10 | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | deadurl = no | title = S04E02: 'Confirmed Dead' | work = ''[[数码间谍|Digital Spy]]'' | accessdate = 2015-09-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927033423/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/s10/lost/review/a89507/s04e02-confirmed-dead.html | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/ustv/s10/lost/review/a89507/s04e02-confirmed-dead.html }}</ref>。

